{"tid":1863050,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"抗疫關係 UA戲院改為隔行賣飛","createTime":"2020-02-05T03:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T16:00:34.000Z","uid":41343,"like":204,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c0e511cd1940adaed986465484239ec5edf932","tid":1863050,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXVqWGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXVqWGq.jpg&h=820c6503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【🛡UA院線加強防疫新安排👩&zwj;🏫】<br />\n<br />\n😌小編同大家一樣都想入場睇戲可以更加安心～<br />\n💁🏼&zwj;♀️放心！全線UA戲院及K11 Art House由2月10日（下周一）起將會加強防疫措施：💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n☝🏻每場放映會以隔行形式售票，坐得鬆動啲，減低觀眾密度，確保每位顧客睇戲時享有更充足嘅空間🙆&zwj;♀️🙆&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n✌🏻全線將於下午2時開始營業🕑，預留更多時間進行全院清潔及消毒。<br />\n<br />\n👌🏻全線繼續嚴格實施「防疫4部曲」🛡（詳細措施：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2GPMevQ），定時進行清潔及消毒工作，更會為每位入場顧客量度體溫🌡*\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GPMevQ%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%9A%E6%99%82%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%8F%8A%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E6%9B%B4%E6%9C%83%E7%82%BA%E6%AF%8F%E4%BD%8D%E5%85%A5%E5%A0%B4%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%94%E6%BA%AB%F0%9F%8C%A1%2A&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcQmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=ecbfccf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2GPMevQ），定時進行清潔及消毒工作，更會為每位入場顧客量度體溫🌡*</a><br />\n<br />\n❗️同時，為保障顧客及員工之健康，顧客於戲院範圍必須佩戴口罩。*<br />\n<br />\n‼️*如顧客有發燒症狀或未有佩戴口罩，本院職員有權拒絕其進場並為顧客進行退款（不包括網上購票手續費）<br />\n<br />\n（以上各項乃臨時措施，將按實際情況作適時修改，售票安排以網上公開發售為準。）<br />\n<br />\n#UACinemas #UAreamused"},{"pid":"8a5509eb6854130483fd7c38dda5df2a4dae4e98","tid":1863050,"uid":74171,"like":348,"dislike":5,"score":343,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:16:16.000Z","msg":"有撚心情睇戲"},{"pid":"668078ae238f15d2809475b89b5941b841637d57","tid":1863050,"uid":77803,"like":226,"dislike":0,"score":226,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T03:17:02.000Z","msg":"左右隔吧啦"},{"pid":"4795a31fb31dbcb107ab08e7a9168de23663f1c8","t